parameters:
Student Eratoma: Father, Mother, I will definitely pass for
the sake of Tarasa and our clan.

Eratoma's mother: You will definitely be able to enroll in
the Magic Academy!

Eratoma's Father: You are the most talented magician in our
clan. Not only for the sake of our family, but also for
Tarasa, give it your all.

Eratoma's Father: In your generation... please defeat the
Demon Empire Fotizona.

Eratoma was born into a prestigious lineage of talented
magicians and was expected to be the most exceptional
magician in generations. What was expected of him was the
victory in a long-lasting war.

The first Tarasa War, which lasted for 8 years, ended with
both sides suffering losses, but considering the self-
sufficiency rate of food and the population ratio, Tarasa
was more deeply affected.

During the era when magic research facilities were being
mass-produced under national leadership, the magic academy
that Eratoma wished to enroll in was among the most
prestigious. Burning with passion for the sake of his family
and the nation, the young man set off on his journey.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
